name: Klaver (The Clover)
description:
Each leaf of clover has a meaning.  The first leaf symbolizes love.  The second strand symbolizes health and longevity.  The third leaf symbolizes the prosperity of life, and the fourth leaf symbolizes abundant wealth.  and in the illustration take a 3 leaf reference, which in my opinion is enough for life.
